# ssh-add-vim

Start ssh-agent on vim. Netrw plugin is useful. But when ssh-agent is still not started, it appear password prompt always.
This plugin start ssh-agent internal.

## Usage

```
:SshAdd
```
You can specify private key file like below:
```
:SshAdd ~/.ssh/my-host
```

